<plot>While on a road trip to Vegas, chain-smoking French coquette Natalie and her effete companion Armand are abducted by aliens. Rather than performing a probe. the aliens seek a probing performance from their captives - something with a "universal" flavor. While filling their bellies. these benign little guys feast their eyes (each only has one) on the show. First up is Armand, who explores his Oedipal proclivities to raucous applause. Then the curtain rises on Natalie. Not your typical intergalactic summer stock, she proceeds to dish up the tastiest entertainment this side of Saturn. Soon, Natalie has her captors eating out of her own hand.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030077</url></doc>
